That is enlarging our
viewpoint, enlarging our world.

00:37:17.080 --> 00:37:21.520 align:middle line:84%
So as we grow, the
world tends to shrink.

00:37:21.520 --> 00:37:23.440 align:middle line:90%
We see the humanity in others.

00:37:23.440 --> 00:37:26.290 align:middle line:84%
We see eyeball to eyeball the
things that people are doing.

00:37:26.290 --> 00:37:29.230 align:middle line:84%
We have a better sense
of the kind of reality

00:37:29.230 --> 00:37:30.350 align:middle line:90%
we're living in.

