And most people don't find
that to be a very good thing.

00:37:35.890 --> 00:37:38.480 align:middle line:84%
They see that this
world is full of fear.

00:37:38.480 --> 00:37:39.910 align:middle line:90%
It's full of nastiness.

00:37:39.910 --> 00:37:40.940 align:middle line:90%
It's full of greed.

00:37:40.940 --> 00:37:42.820 align:middle line:84%
It's full of people
out for themselves.

