happens, and the high priests

00:38:39.910 --> 00:38:44.410 align:middle line:84%
put us into the mainstream with
that concept of what we're here

00:38:44.410 --> 00:38:47.680 align:middle line:84%
to do is grow up,
become love, then

00:38:47.680 --> 00:38:52.150 align:middle line:84%
people who are fed up
with greed and avarice

00:38:52.150 --> 00:38:54.730 align:middle line:90%
