00:38:54.730 --> 00:38:57.700 align:middle line:84%
This idea of a virtual
reality, this idea

00:38:57.700 --> 00:39:01.750 align:middle line:84%
that I have in "My Big
Toe," it's very inclusive.

00:39:01.750 --> 00:39:04.460 align:middle line:90%
Everybody can be a part of it.

00:39:04.460 --> 00:39:06.250 align:middle line:84%
It's not something
you have to believe.

00:39:06.250 --> 00:39:08.770 align:middle line:84%
Matter of fact, I say
belief is a problem.

00:39:08.770 --> 00:39:10.390 align:middle line:90%
Ego and belief are problems.

00:39:10.390 --> 00:39:12.100 align:middle line:90%
Always be skeptical.

00:39:12.100 --> 00:39:14.320 align:middle line:84%
But it's something
that opposites

00:39:14.320 --> 00:39:16.330 align:middle line:90%
