In other words, if
you're an atheist,

00:39:18.670 --> 00:39:20.800 align:middle line:84%
you can look at the "My
Big Toe" and you can say,

00:39:20.800 --> 00:39:22.990 align:middle line:90%
ah, knew it all along.

