00:39:33.970 --> 00:39:35.860 align:middle line:84%
This larger
consciousness system.

00:39:35.860 --> 00:39:37.090 align:middle line:90%
That's God.

00:39:37.090 --> 00:39:41.980 align:middle line:84%
So people from all sides
can find a logical structure

00:39:41.980 --> 00:39:44.860 align:middle line:84%
that they can hang
their own experience on.

00:39:44.860 --> 00:39:48.220 align:middle line:84%
And when that
happens, I think we'll

00:39:48.220 --> 00:39:52.120 align:middle line:84%
